abstract: A force of 800 insurgents was marching on Panama at the latest dates, May 15, and a battle was imminent, as the Government troops intended to offer a stout resistance. A steamer on the Magdalena River exploded her boilers recently, killing fourteen persons.

abstract: The jury in the trial of DAVID MONTGOMERY for the murder of his wife, in November last, in Rochester, N.Y., retired about 3 o'clock Tuesday afternoon. The jury emained out all Wednesday night, and came into Court, yesterday, with a verdict of guilty of murder in the first degree. The defense was insanity. The prisoner was remanded for sentence on the second Monday in June next.
